{"tha-ap480:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap480:0.2":"Nalamalivagga ","tha-ap480:0.3":"Vallikaraphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap480:1.1":"“Sumano nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap480:1.2":"takkarayam vasi tada; ","tha-ap480:1.3":"Vallikaraphalam gayha, ","tha-ap480:1.4":"sayambhussa adasaham. ","tha-ap480:2.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap480:2.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap480:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap480:2.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap480:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap480:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap480:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap480:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap480:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap480:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap480:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap480:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap480:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap480:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma vallikaraphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap480:7.1":"Vallikaraphaladayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}